Interface FeIscListener

public interface FeIscListener

This interface provides event signaling from this package to an application.

Field Detail

TRANSCEIVE_STRING_EVENT

static final int TRANSCEIVE_STRING_EVENT
Event-ID for signaling the transmit and receive protocol strings to the application.
This ID combines the events SEND_STRING_EVENT and RECEIVE_STRING_EVENT.
Every event calls its own listener method.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

SEND_STRING_EVENT

static final int SEND_STRING_EVENT
Event-ID for signaling the transmit protocol string to the application.
The protocol string is a parameter of the listener method onSendProtocol.
